	<h1>Combining Components</h1>

	This page demonstrates how components can be combined to create new components.<br/><br/>

	In this example we combine SlidingPanel with SourceCodeDisplay to produce a new component, <strong>SlidingSourceCodeDisplay</strong>.<br/>
	It renders a SlidingPanel wrapped around a SourceCodeDisplay.<br/> 
	SlidingPanel was explained in the Third Party Components example. SourceCodeDisplay is a JumpStart component.<br/> 
	Our new component requires a <em>src</em> parameter, whose value it passes directly into SourceCodeDisplay.<br/><br/>

	For more components see <em>Third Party Libraries</em> on <a href="http://tapestry.apache.org/tapestry5/">Tapestry 5 Home</a>
	and <em>Components</em> on <a href="http://wiki.apache.org/tapestry/Tapestry5HowTos">Tapestry 5 How Tos</a>.<br/><br/>
	
